	<li><a href="<%Response.write href_pre%>dependentcare.asp" class="left2" onfocus="this.className='left2-over';" onblur="this.className='left2';" title="Dependent care programs">Dependent care programs</a><br>
Programs designed to help you locate and pay for quality dependent care for children and aging parents.<br><br></li>
	<li><b>Adoption reimbursement</b><br>Helps you pay for an adoption and related expenses.<br>
	<p style="padding-left: 18px; margin: 4px 0px 4px 0px;">How it works:</p>
	<p style="padding-left: 18px; margin: 0px 0px 0px 0px;">You pay your adoption expenses and, upon legal adoption, you may be reimbursed by Bank of America up to $8,000 per adopted child.</p>
	<br></li>
	<li><a href="<%Response.write href_pre%>timeoff.asp" class="left2" onfocus="this.className='left2-over';" onblur="this.className='left2';" title="Time off">Time off</a><br>
You'll receive time off on a paid and/or unpaid basis depending on your need and eligibility.<br><br></li>
	<li><a href="<%Response.write href_pre%>educationinit.asp" class="left2" onfocus="this.className='left2-over';" onblur="this.className='left2';" title="Education initiatives">Education initiatives</a><br>
Includes scholarships, tuition reimbursement and paid volunteer time for school.<br><br></li>
	<li><a href="http://www.bankofamerica.com/teambank/" target="_blank" class="left2" onfocus="this.className='left2-over';" onblur="this.className='left2';" title="Team Bank of America">Team Bank of America</a><br>
